Rowdy Wolf mused at Zyber. They were nearly in the same case.

He asked: "Have you ever met any bots before?" He looked at her face. "Did 
you ever wonder who you really were?" He grinned and snickered. "I just 
thought I was a bizzare species before I met that Predacon a while ago."
